  ../../forge_worktrees/2624-42f8dc6a/skills/review-library-update-request/SKILL.md:17:- Do not require `library-new-request`'s minimum dynamic-access threshold. A library update can be acceptable with low coverage if the percentage did not regress and the requested issue work is covered.
